pe":"Activities::BugResolved","message":"Thanks a lot for your report. This has been fixed now by updating the used Docker container for Discourse.\n\nDiscourse was shipping a vulnerable version of Nginx until container version 1.3.4 (https://github.com/discourse/discourse_docker/commit/e8b9677b79e06b8864d87407b77e7800dc6c10f5) . We have fixed this by updating the container as described at https://meta.discourse.org/t/how-do-i-update-my-docker-image-to-latest/23325\n\n```\ncd /var/discourse\ngit pull\n./launcher rebuild app\n```\n\nA quick check verifies that we're indeed running 1.10.1 now:\n\n```\nroot@help-app:/var/www/discourse# nginx -v\nnginx version: nginx/1.10.1\n```\n\nThanks a lot for reporting this to us!\n\n","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2016-06-27T20:50:35.384Z","updated_at":"2016-06-27T20:58:55.729Z","actor":{"username":"lukasreschke","cleared":false,"url":"/lukasreschke","profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/037/891/e7fea4d5383dc07d1fe767b02f3bda2bc7639c63_original.png/fd4ecbe1e3e98c343c7717114485ace2f830f9253103d3cfa7502059868c516c"},"hackerone_triager":false,"hackerone_employee":false},"reporter":{"username":"shoveller","url":"/shoveller"},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handle":"nextcloud","actor_is_team_member":false,"actor_is_concealed_member":false},{"id":1041663,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::NotEligibleForBounty","message":"As per our current bug bounty brief our web services are excluded from monetary rewards.","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2016-06-27T20:50:59.071Z","updated_at":"2016-06-27T20:50:59.071Z","actor":{"url":"/nextcloud","ibb":false,"profile_picture_urls":{"medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/000/013/291/68f57538488b5716cdeeb6b78955f9e46685bc09_original.png/fd4ecbe1e3e98c343c7717114485ace2f830f9253103d3cfa7502059868c516c"},"profile":{"name":"Nextcloud"}},"genius_execution_id":null,"team_handl